Text-Stripper version 1.16
==========================


DESCRIPTION

Text::Stripper shortens text and avoids cutting the text in the middle
of a word.


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install


DEPENDENCIES

- at least Perl 5.6.1


